ave your legs shaking!", "short_description": "Welcome to Mars!\nAs experienced at World Expo 2020 (October 2021) in Dubai you now have the possibility to take your first steps on the surface of planet Mars.\nMarsQuest is a short experience, recommended for groups between 5 to 15 people.\nYou, as an Event Master, need to set up the environment so it becomes fun for the ones you will show it to. Before setup, we recommend you to set the guardian warning system to a minimum.\nMarsQuest is an experience that will have your legs shaking!"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.imitera.com/privacy-policy-marsquest/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Imitera AB", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.imitera.com/", "category": "ENTERTAINMENT", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["TRAVEL", "SPACE_UNIVERSE", "CASUAL"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["HAND_TRACKING", "OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "463625768636526"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 3, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "496203874875316"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "333137849122701"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "552553896255952"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "333137849122701"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1639065720, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "496203874875316"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "51318